title: 'He likes to hit': How Packers' Tucker Kraft is eliciting comparisons to Mark Bavaro, tight ends of yore
description: Mark Bavaro says Kraft is playing tight end "the way I was brought up to play it."
author: Rob Demovsky

title: Ultimate Rizz: Saints' Darren Rizzi is staying true to himself in head coaching quest
description: The New Orleans interim coach is seizing his seven-game audition in hopes of fulfilling his lifelong dream.
author: Katherine Terrell

title: Cross loses as record number of seeds out of Worlds
description: Former champion Rob Cross is knocked out of the 2025 World Darts Championships as a record number of seeds fall in the second round at Alexandra Palace.

title: How Sir Alex Ferguson built his last great Manchester United side

title: Cross and Chisnall suffer shock exits in marathon Ally Pally session
description: Dave Chisnall crashed out of the World Darts Championship after suffering a dramatic final-leg loss to Ricky Evans, while former world champion Rob Cross was also dumped out in a remarkable session at Alexandra Palace.

title: Stokes out for at least three months with torn hamstring
description: Ben Stokes has been ruled out of all cricket for at least three months due to a torn left hamstring.

title: Live updates: Packers can clinch playoff spot with win over Saints
description: Green Bay is in third place in the NFL's most loaded conference, the NFC North, but it will punch its postseason ticket unless New Orleans pulls off the upset.

title: Steph calls out fan after Dubs-Wolves for stealing shoes from kid
description: Warriors superstar Steph Curry called out a fan for stealing his game-worn shoes from a child after Golden State's win over the Minnesota Timberwolves.
author: NBC Sports BayArea
